Class GameCupoun

  • java.lang.Object
    • by.epamtr.totalizator.bean.entity.GameCupoun

    public class GameCupoun
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class is designed to represent the game coupon's entity. Game coupon represents the drawing of the totalizator that lasts for a week. Users are allowed to make bets on particular game coupons.
